#. module: l10n_do_accounting_report
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:l10n_do_accounting_report.field_account_bank_statement_line__fiscal_status
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:l10n_do_accounting_report.field_account_move__fiscal_status
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:l10n_do_accounting_report.field_account_payment__fiscal_status
msgid ""
"* The 'Grey' status means invoice isn't fully reported and may appear in other report if a withholding is applied.\n"
"* The 'Green' status means invoice is fully reported.\n"
"* The 'Red' status means invoice is included in a non sent DGII report.\n"
"* The blank status means that the invoice haven't been included in a report."
msgstr ""
"* El estado 'Gris' significa que la factura no está completamente reportada y puede aparecer en otro informe si se aplica una retención.\n"
"* El estado 'Verde' significa que la factura está completamente reportada.\n"
"* El estado 'Rojo' significa que la factura está incluida en un informe DGII no enviado.\n"
"* El estado en blanco significa que la factura no ha sido incluida en un informe."

